<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM2.7.5">
<l>ōtilu muṉpē raṉṟimaṟ ṟōtā ḷurukuniṉ tiruvuru niṉaintu</l>
<l>kātaṉmai peritu kaiyaṟa vuṭaiyaḷ kayalneṭuṅ kaṇtuyil maṟantāḷ</l>
<l>pētaiyēṉ pētai piḷḷaimai peritu teḷḷiyaḷ vaḷḷinuṇ maruṅkul</l>
<l>ētalar muṉṉā veṉṉiṉain tiruntā yiṭaventai yentaipi rāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if she speaks, she does not speak anything but your name;</l>
<l rend="indent">she melts, thinking of your divine form.</l>
<l>[Her] desire is great. She who is broken-hearted shuns sleep</l>
<l rend="indent">[for her] long carp[-like] eyes.</l>
<l>The childish innocence of this fool of mine, I being a fool, is great,</l>
<l rend="indent">[yet] she is wise.</l>
<l>In front of those who fault [this] thin creeper-waisted [girl],</l>
<l rend="indent">what were you intending, lord father of Iṭaventai?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
